caption.title: Bayesian skyline plots of effective population sizes for the main HIV-1 strains among MSM in Yunnan.
caption.p: A, Bayesian skyline plot of effective population size for CRF01_AE; B, Bayesian skyline plot of effective population size for CRF07_BC. The black line represents the median effective population size over time. The dotted lines represent the lower and higher bounds of the 95% highest posterior density interval.
